Job Description 
 
We are currently looking for experienced software professionals interested in joining our team. We are passionate developers that care about practicing contemporary coding practices like: TDD, pairing, clean code, polyglot programming etc. At Icosystem we work on projects where performance matters, and domain modeling is critical. We are highly creative, self-directed and value critical thinking. 
 
At Icosystem, you will work closely with our scientists on short-medium term projects for commercial companies, philanthropic non-profits, and the government, delivering prototypes and running simulations/predictive models to our clients. Our developers work primarily in Scala and Java, on small teams and have the opportunity to work on all tiers of an application, from front-end UIs to back-end databases. 
 
